<HEADLINE> Cambodia Not to Compete at Nagano Olympics </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, July 18 (Xinhua) -- Cambodia will not send athletes to
compete at next year's Winter Olympic Games in Nagano, Japan,
organisers said on Friday.
</P>
<P>
The Nagano Olympic Winter Games Organizing Committee (NAOC)
said it had received a fax from the International Olympic
Committee (IOC) "indicating withdrawal" of Cambodia, who had said
it would join the biggest winter sports event.
</P>
