<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, July 18 (Xinhua)-- India has secured the United
Nations Security Council's approval to export 1,000 tons of tea to
Iraq under the "oil-for-food" program, a senior official of the
Indian Commerce Ministry said today.
