Grossman defeating Nickitas 6-0, 7-6 (7-3) and Lettiere prevailing
over Tami Whitlinger-Jones, who retired with injury trailing 3-6.
</P>
<P>
Likhovtseva fought back from one set down to eliminate another
American Ginger Helgeson Neilsen 3-6, 6-2, 6-4. 
