<TEXT>
<P>
CHANGCHUN, July 18 (Xinhua) -- The people of Changchun will no
longer stop each other on the street to ask for the time now that
300 big clocks have been installed along three of the city's major
thoroughfares.
</P>
<P>
The unique-shaped clocks have been ticking off the minutes for
the public in this capital city of northeastern Jilin Province
since mid-June.
</P>
<P>
