However, ASEAN foreign ministers decided at a special meeting
here on July 10 to defer the admission of Cambodia into ASEAN in
view of the armed conflicts between supporters of Ranariddh and
Hun Sen.
</P>
<P>
ASEAN currently groups Brunei, Indonesia, Malaysia, the
Philippines, Singapore, Thailand and Vietnam.  
