<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, July 18 (Xinhua) -- Nepali Finance Minister Rabindra
Nath Sharma said here Thursday that the Nepali government is
committed to formulate a long-term export policy and promote
quality improvement of exports, local press reports said today.
</P>
<P>
Inaugurating a two-day seminar on networking of trade related
research institutions in Nepal, Sharma said in order to develop
trade as a vehicle for growth, the government is ready to improve
