foreign brokerage companies in Bangkok on suspicion they started
the rumor that five local commercial banks are on the verge of
collapse.
</P>
<P>
About 30 city policemen, half in plainclothes, raided Abn-Amro
Hoare Govett and Capital Nomura securities brokerage firms and
left with three large files, according to the local press today.
